DESCRIPTION >
    Configuration for anomaly detection thresholds

SCHEMA >
    `metric` String `json:$.metric`,
    `service` String `json:$.service`,
    `threshold_value` Float64 `json:$.threshold_value`,
    `threshold_type` String `json:$.threshold_type`,
    `updated_at` DateTime `json:$.updated_at`

ENGINE "MergeTree"
ENGINE_PARTITION_KEY "metric"
ENGINE_SORTING_KEY "metric, service"